âš¡ Learning Flow:

1. Start with Angular-only small projects (Portfolio, To-Do)


2. Add Spring Boot APIs (Notes App)


3. Implement Security (Auth System)


4. Learn DB relations (Blog/E-Commerce)


5. Explore Real-Time (Chat)


6. End with Deployment




